# Wardrobe Label Print Server Configuration

This file contains environment variables for the application.

## Database Configuration
DB_SERVER=av-sql2
DB_DATABASE=Wardrobe01Prod
DB_USERNAME=Wardrobe
DB_PASSWORD=FQq@Y67*Vaim
DB_ENCRYPT=false
DB_TRUST_CERT=true
DB_CONNECT_TIMEOUT=30000

## Printer Configuration
PRINTER_IP=10.2.1.61
PRINTER_PORT=9100

## Application Configuration
NODE_ENV=development
LOG_LEVEL=info
POLLING_INTERVAL=5000

## Notes
- POLLING_INTERVAL is in milliseconds (default: 5000ms = 5 seconds)
- Change LOG_LEVEL to 'debug' for more verbose logging
- For production, set NODE_ENV=production
